Package org.gvsig.remoteClient.arcims

Class Summary
ArcImsClientP Abstract class the with the necessary logic to connect to a ArcIms and interpretate the data.
ArcImsFeatureClient Class that connects with ArcIMS and retrieves a Feature Layer
ArcImsImageClient Concrete class to deal with an ArcIMS ImageServer
ArcImsProtFeatureHandler  
ArcImsProtImageHandler Describes the handler to communicate to a ArcIMS ImageServer
ArcImsProtocolHandler Abstract class that represents handlers to comunicate via ArcIms protocol
ArcImsProtocolHandlerFactory Factory to create a proper handler based on the service type (ImageServer of FeatureServer)
ArcImsStatus Describes the status of a ArcImsclient, so it adds to the Remote client status a list of layers, a list of layer styles, the extent of the map.
ArcImsStyle Defines a style.
ArcImsVectStatus Extended class to implement specific vectorial state information
ArcXML Class that provides static methods to generate general ArcXML requests
ArcXMLFeatures  
ArcXMLImage Class that provides static methods to generate ImageServer related ArcXML requests
